{"tid":2508681,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登：美國歡迎與中國競爭 不尋求衝突","createTime":"2021-04-29T02:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T02:55:14.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9754e2bce510dce5434d6770f978ec22d09115b4","tid":2508681,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:50:03.000Z","msg":"拜登：美國歡迎與中國競爭　不尋求衝突<br />\n<br />\n美國總統拜登在上任一百日的前夕，首度到國會參眾兩院發表演說。<br />\n<br />\n拜登在演說中談及美中關係，他表示，美國歡迎與中國競爭，不尋求衝突。拜登強調，將會在印太地區維持強大軍事影響力，就像美國為北約在歐洲所做的一樣。<br />\n<br />\n拜登又表示，美國將加強應對國有企業補貼及竊取美國技術及知識產權等不公平的貿易行為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588340-20210429.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588340-20210429.htm&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=26d3430a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588340-20210429.htm&h=afedf762\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588340-20210429.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ccc4816fe0da9878072d9ce335d67520d2b0c3f1","tid":2508681,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:51:06.000Z","msg":"將會在印太地區維持強大軍事影響力，就像美國為北約在歐洲所做的一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0385f8f1bd0acdb5407f4a1c9e2a3b7a3cf766ab","tid":2508681,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:52:30.000Z","msg":"中美和好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4110108b52c018547edbde1523fcf53e4ed36d8d","tid":2508681,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:53:07.000Z","msg":"完全係配合中共個套講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n競乜撚野爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c114a57d2338f54e7d5cfc8681320bca241712f","tid":2508681,"uid":59929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:53:29.000Z","msg":"講一套做一套啫<br />\n美國不尋求同中國衝突就插架軍艦入中國戰鬥群<br />\n中國要做戰狼但人地插左入黎莫講話打聲都唔敢出"},{"pid":"f137537db6a0b9e8e0b9658b896b1df2a86e8047","tid":2508681,"uid":186882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ccc4816fe0da9878072d9ce335d67520d2b0c3f1","tid":2508681,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:51:06.000Z","msg":"將會在印太地區維持強大軍事影響力，就像美國為北約在歐洲所做的一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T02:55:14.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭：「拜登我屌你老母，再唔幫拖我哋整核彈自救。」"}]}